### Add comment to an article
PUT http://localhost:4000/user-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user":"698d2b0210353dc78e6e6e15",
  "articleId":"69cb7686360a560082ba7530",
  "comment":"This is a very insightful article! I appreciate the depth of analysis and the practical examples provided. It has given me a lot to think about regarding the future of AI in finance. Thank you for sharing your expertise on this topic!"
 
}


### Admin APIs
### Register admin
POST http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Admin1",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "admin1@gmail.com",
  "password": "Admin1@123",
  "role": "ADMIN",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://png.pngtree.com/png-vector/20221125/ourmid/pngtree-host-and-admin-marketing-job-vacancies-vector-png-image_6480101.png"
}
### Admin Login
POST http://localhost:4000/common-api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin1@gmail.com",
  "password": "Admin1@123"
}
### Read all articles
GET http://localhost:4000/admin-api/articles

### Read all users
GET http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users

### Block user
PUT http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users/69cb7585360a560082ba7527/block
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "69cb7585360a560082ba7527"
}

### Unblock user
PUT http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users/69cb7585360a560082ba7527/unblock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "69cb7585360a560082ba7527"
}

### Delete or restore article
PATCH http://localhost:4000/admin-api/articles/698d3a41ba3c49843f1146e5/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isArticleActive": true
}



